data.description: Looking for the perfect starter home or investment property? Look no further. This spacious brick home, on all four sides, is it. Room for everyone, a nice patio overlooking the pretty backyard. Inside there are 2 baths. Central HVAC and more. Lots of cabinets and countertops in the kitchen. An indoor laundry room makes laundry so much better than going out to a hot or cold garage. The carport is part of the roof structure.
